<template>

<v-container>

  <v-row>

        color="primary"
        @click="passFilter()"
       >Apply Filter</v-btn>

<script>

export default {
  name: 'FilterListing',
  data() {
    return {
      category: ''
    }
  },
  methods: {
    passFilter: function() {
      console.log(this.category)
      this.$emit('applyFilter', this.category)
    }
  }
}
</script>
